## DIAGRAM 2: User Journey Loop (Builder Comment Cycle)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start["🎬 START: Architect Creates Project"] --> Upload["📤 UPLOAD<br/>Architect uploads drawing<br/>Status: Draft<br/>All team notified"]
    
    Upload --> Assign["📋 ASSIGN<br/>PM assigns drawing to Builder<br/>Notification sent"]
    
    Assign --> Review["👀 REVIEW<br/>Builder views drawing on-site<br/>Identifies issue"]
    
    Review --> Comment{"💬 COMMENT<br/>Builder marks PDF:<br/>'Rebar spacing unclear here'"}
    
    Comment --> NotifyArch["🔔 Architect notified<br/>Comment appears in dashboard"]
    
    NotifyArch --> Revise["✏️ REVISE<br/>Architect uploads new version<br/>Old version auto-archived"]
    
    Revise --> Ready{"✅ READY?<br/>PM reviews revised drawing"}
    
    Ready -->|"Issues Found"| Comment
    Ready -->|"Approved"| MarkReady["🟢 MARK READY<br/>PM sets status: Ready for Execution<br/>Notification sent to Builder"]
    
    MarkReady --> Execute["🔨 EXECUTE<br/>Builder on-site marks drawing Executed<br/>Timestamp logged"]
    
    Execute --> Archive["🗄️ ARCHIVE<br/>Drawing locked<br/>Comments preserved<br/>Full audit trail stored"]
    
    Archive --> End["🏁 END: Drawing Complete<br/>Loop repeats for next drawing"]
    
    End -.->|"Next Drawing"| Upload
    
    style Start fill:#4CAF50,stroke:#2E7D32,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Execute fill:#FF5722,stroke:#BF360C,stroke-width:3px,color:#fff
    style Archive fill:#607D8B,stroke:#37474F,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style End fill:#4CAF50,stroke:#2E7D32,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Comment fill:#FF9800,stroke:#E65100,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style MarkReady fill:#2196F3,stroke:#1565C0,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
```

